Too many house sales collapse late in the process, causing financial loss, stress, and wasted costs. Introduce binding agreements, clearer timelines, and penalties for unjustified withdrawal to reduce failures, improve confidence, and create a fairer, home-buying process across the UK.
Review the current residential property transaction process;
Consult with consumers, conveyancers, lenders, and estate agents;
Introduce legislation to bring forward legal commitment during property transactions;
